column2: "Hello there. I've noticed you've been working really hard recently."
"Honestly, if you keep that pace up, you may make it to the council of six someday."
"Right now their power is beyond comparison but it's not like they were always like that."
"It's only after endless determination and dedication that they were able to come this far."
"...well, Claris Claes is a little different. Actually, no she doesn't fit that description at all."
"Come to think of it, I don't really care for hard work either...."
